{"tid":760082,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 可愛韓妹每一場表演的表情都令人溶化","createTime":"2018-07-29T08:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T15:09:54.000Z","uid":74065,"like":9,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"91e979fab6f34add21661c321acb7b8c7a5f30aa","tid":760082,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:05:29.000Z","msg":"韓國偶像在回歸之前，都要經歷數十次到百次的練習，才能呈現完美的舞台，這也是為什麼幾乎每一團都能跳出刀群舞的主要原因。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE的多賢就被發現之前以《LIKEY》活動時，幾乎每場的歪頭程度、笑容、表情都完全一模一樣啊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/550/2017/12/06/550_1108712_1512554383.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F550_1108712_1512554383.webp&h=e7e4d63d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/550/2017/12/06/550_1108718_1512554503.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F550_1108718_1512554503.webp&h=4b93fcb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/550/2017/12/06/550_1108721_1512554567.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F550_1108721_1512554567.webp&h=98c3b2e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/550/2017/12/06/550_1108730_1512554691.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F550_1108730_1512554691.webp&h=798d4e36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/550/2017/12/06/550_1108736_1512554899.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F550_1108736_1512554899.webp&h=14005afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face